"<h1>頁面源代碼</h1>\n\n<div class=\"page-source\">\n\t[[&gt;]]<br />\n[[module Rate]]<br />\n[[/&gt;]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;attribution&quot;]]<br />\nArtwork by [[[aethris-art|Aethris]]]<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[module CSS]]<br />\nhtml, body {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;overflow-x: hidden;<br />\n}<br />\n.attribution {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;text-transform: uppercase;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;font-weight: bold;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;font-size: 0.8em;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;position: absolute;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;top: -20px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;z-index: 10;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;text-align: right;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;right: -100px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;white-space: nowrap;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;overflow: hidden;<br />\n}<br />\n.attribution p {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin: 0;<br />\n}<br />\n#main-content::before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 600px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;width: 1200px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;content: &quot;&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-image: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/end-of-death-hub/eod_new_small_preload.png);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-size: cover;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;position: relative;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;display: block;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-position: center;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-left: calc(-80px - 22em - 1em);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-top: calc(-600px - 1em);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;z-index: 1;<br />\n}<br />\n#content-wrap::before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 600px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;width: 1200px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;content: &quot;&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-image: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/end-of-death-hub/eod_new_large.png), url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/end-of-death-hub/eod_new_large_preload.png);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-size: cover, cover;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;position: relative;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;display: block;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-position: center, center;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-left: -80px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;z-index: 2;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;animation: 2s ease-in-out 0s 1 fadeIn;<br />\n}<br />\n#content-wrap::after {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 600px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;width: 1200px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;content: &quot;&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;position: absolute;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;display: block;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;top: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0) 0, rgba(0,0,0,0) 450px, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 550px, rgba(255,255,255,1) 600px, rgba(255,255,255,1) 1200px);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-left: -80px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;animation: 2s ease-out 0s 1 swipeDown;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-position: 0 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-size: 1200px 1200px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0,0.7,0.31,0.96);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;z-index: 3;<br />\n}<br />\n@keyframes swipeDown {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;0% {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-position: 0 -300px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;100% {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-position: 0 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br />\n}<br />\n@keyframes swipeDownMobile {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;0% {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/*background-position: 0 -25vw;*/<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-position: 0 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;100% {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-position: 0 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br />\n}<br />\n@keyframes fadeIn {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;0% {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;opacity: 0.01;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;100% {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;opacity: 1;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br />\n}<br />\n#content-wrap {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;position: relative;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-top: 0;<br />\n}<br />\n#side-bar {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-top: 600px;<br />\n}<br />\n@media only screen and (max-width: 1200px) {<br />\n#content-wrap::before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 300px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;width: 100%;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-repeat: no-repeat;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-left: auto;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-right: auto;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;animation: none;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-position: 0 30%;<br />\n}<br />\n#main-content::before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;display: none;<br />\n}<br />\n#content-wrap::after {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 300px;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;width: 100%;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;top: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0) 0, rgba(0,0,0,0) 225px, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 275px, rgba(255,255,255,1) 300px, rgba(255,255,255,1) 600px);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-left: auto;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-right: auto;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-position: 0 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-size: 600px 600px;<br />\n}<br />\n#side-bar {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-top: 300px;<br />\n}<br />\n.attribution {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;right: calc(50vw - 300px - 2em);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;right: -2em;<br />\n}<br />\n}<br />\n@media only screen and (max-width: 700px) {<br />\n#content-wrap::before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 50vw;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-size: 100vw 50vw;<br />\n}<br />\n#content-wrap::after {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 25vw;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-image: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/end-of-death-hub/eod_new_medium.png);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-size: 100vw 50vw;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0) 0, rgba(0,0,0,0) 19vw, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 22vw, rgba(255,255,255,1) 25vw, rgba(255,255,255,1) 50vw);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;animation: 2s ease-out 0s 1 swipeDownMobile;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;top: 25vw<br />\n}<br />\n.attribution {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;right: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;box-shadow: 0 0 5px 5px #fff;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: #fff;<br />\n}<br />\n#page-title {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;padding-top: 1em;<br />\n}<br />\n}<br />\n[[/module]]<br />\n<br />\n[[toc]]<br />\n<br />\n&gt; [[=]]<br />\n&gt; **節錄自基金會數據庫「K級意外事故」**<br />\n&gt; [[/=]]<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; -----<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; **情景類型：**ΩK級<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; **發生率：**近幾不可能<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; **嚴重性：**仍適合生存，但人類文明須經適度重建<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; **描述：**ΩK 級情景(「死亡終了」)是指所有生命體於不伴隨其它生理變化(例如停止老化或強制絕育)之情況下，獲得無法死亡之特性。該情景的發生意指已免除任何破碎假面情景造成的可能，且基金會及其支部仍維持當前格局。<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; **應對程序：**<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; 1. //數量控制：//基於昆蟲的出生及死亡率，該行動須於情景發生的二十四小時後解決，否則昆蟲數目將超過 WK 級情景之閥值。以上為該行動中最關鍵之時刻，於此之後，必須為其餘物種籌備長期解決方案。<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; 2. //情報掌控：//儘管此時人口總數已處於異常情況，仍必須確保其餘異常現象仍處於隱蔽狀態，而原先無異常之事物因 ΩK 級情景之影響，須重新評估其狀態，遏止行動亦須持續進行，對外則以散佈偽造學術言論以解釋新發現的不朽現象。<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; 3. //應對終局之替補方案：//若已無實質上的死亡，基於道德因素，必須針對此項策畫替代方案。任人類無限期蒙受腐敗器官所苦為無法接受之結果。<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n[[=]]<br />\n+ 第一季<br />\n[[/=]]<br />\n<br />\n**JOYCE MICHAELS 博士的研究**<br />\n# **[[[*In The Clutches Of Life |]]]** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n# **[[[SCP-3984]]] - 用棍棒戳死神** by //Croquembouche//<br />\n# **[[[omega-k|ΩK]]]** by //Croquembouche//<br />\n# **[[[surgical-identity-perpetuation|GRANT REQUEST FOR THE PERFECTION OF BRAIN TRANSPLANTS FOR IDENTITY PERPETUATION AS TREATMENT FOR AGE-IMPAIRED IMMORTALITY]]]** by //Veiedhimaedhr//<br />\n# **[[[With The Reaper On Retirement]]]** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n# **[[[the foundation wants a robot army|Tales Of The Ethics Committee: 5 Reasons The Foundation Wants A Robot Army]]]** by //Captain Kirby//, //OthellotheCat//, //Veiedhimaedhr// and //Croquembouche//<br />\n# **[[[SCP-3448]]] - Halfterlife** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n<br />\n**相關文件**<br />\n* **[[[SCP-3287]]] - Anti-Baby Gas** by //OthellotheCat//<br />\n* **[[[populated-control-led|Population Control(led)]]]** by //OthellotheCat//<br />\n* **[[[SCP-3866]]] - Youth in Asia by dado** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n* **[[[societal-census-programme|Excerpts From The Societal Census Programme ΩK-Class Report]]]** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n* **[[[hypnotraline|'Hypnotraline' (TR7K2/2UD9X/53GN8)]]]** by //Veiedhimaedhr//<br />\n* **[[[ii tab po c h20 qhs prn pain]]]** by //Veiedhimaedhr//<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n&gt; //**閱讀順序**//<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; //[[[*In The Clutches Of Life | 於生命的魔掌中]]]應優先，而其餘皆交互牽涉，因此可按個人興趣隨意閱讀──看到陌生的標題，點下去就對了！//<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; //記得確認該篇確實貼上「死亡終了」世界線中心的標籤！//<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n[[=]]<br />\n+ 第二季<br />\n[[/=]]<br />\n<br />\n**EMILY YOUNG 博士的研究**<br />\n# **[[[SCP-4514]]] - 殺死你的東西** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n# **[[[Do You Remember Funerals?]]]** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n# **[[[Hundred-Year Favor]]]** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n# **[[[Project Damn-Oh-Fuck|Project Damnerung]]]** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n# **[[[Where Death Used To Live]]]** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n# **[[[From The Clutches Of Life]]]** by //Captain Kirby//<br />\n<br />\n**VIOLET MESMUR 博士的研究**<br />\n# **[[[new-buteo-series-mechanical-exoskeleton|Anderson Robotics' Installation Guide: Your New Buteo Series Mechanical Exoskeleton!]]]** by //OthellotheCat//<br />\n# **[[[Eat Your Greenes]]]** by //OthellotheCat//<br />\n# **[[[SCP-4725]]] - The Insurgency's Solution** by //OthellotheCat//<br />\n# **[[[the-doctor-s-dilemma|The Doctor's Dilemma]]]** by //FloppyPhoenix//<br />\n# 敬請期待<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n[[=]]<br />\n+ 珀耳塞福涅[[footnote]] (譯者註)希臘神話中冥神之妻[[/footnote]]計畫<br />\n[[/=]]<br />\n<br />\n**KAIN PATHOS CROW 教授的研究**<br />\n# **[[[digging-up-the-past|Digging Up The Past]]]** by //Gabriel Jade// and //Uncle Nicolini.//<br />\n# **[[[who-wants-to-live-forever|Who Wants To Live Forever?]]]** by //Gabriel Jade// and //Uncle Nicolini.//<br />\n# **[[[the-hermit-death-and-the-devil|The Hermit, Death, and The Devil]]]** by //Gabriel Jade// and //Uncle Nicolini.//<br />\n# **[[[persephone-project|Persephone Project]]]** by //Gabriel Jade// and //Uncle Nicolini.//<br />\n# 敬請期待<br />\n<br />\n**相關文件**<br />\n* **[[[omega-k-049|SCP-049-ΩK]]]** by //Uncle Nicolini//<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n<br />\n[[=]]<br />\n+ 一個世界死後的故事<br />\n[[/=]]<br />\n<br />\n